===Tampa Bay Bucanneers===
Herron was taken in the sixth round with the 185th overall pick of the [[2014 NFL Draft]] by the [[Tampa Bay Buccaneers]].

Herron was waived by Buccaneers on September 1, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150903182225/http://www.buccaneers.com/news/article-smith/Bucs-Get-to-75-Man-Roster-Limit/08343800-3453-4dc5-86a0-cab219469864|title=Bucs Get to 75-Man Roster Limit|date=September 1, 2015|first=Scott|last=Smith|work=Buccaneers.com|accessdate=January 1, 2016}}</ref>

===Miami Dolphins===
The [[Miami Dolphins]] signed Herron to their [[practice squad]] on October 14, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.miamidolphins.com/news/article-1/NOTEBOOK-Battle-Lines-Drawn-At-Right-Guard-Other-Notes/363505d2-06e0-4a03-8e7b-3dc85f2b1197|title=Notebook: Battle Lines Drawn At Right Guard; Other Notes|date=October 14, 2015|first=Alain|last=Poupart|work=MiamiDolphins.com|accessdate=January 2, 2016}}</ref> On January 6, 2016, Herron signed a reserve/future contract with the [[Miami Dolphins]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.miamidolphins.com/news/press-releases/article-1/PRESS-RELEASE-Dolphins-Sign-Eight-Players-To-ReserveFuture-Contracts/858f5bab-f1bc-491b-a5a6-71f6080039e0|title=PRESS RELEASE: Dolphins Sign Eight Players To Reserve/Future Contracts|website=www.miamidolphins.com|access-date=2016-05-14}}</ref> On April 28, he was waived.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.miamidolphins.com/news/press-releases/article-1/PRESS-RELEASE-Dolphins-Make-Roster-Moves/7b38296e-3e43-4f1b-a501-f5ed063bc9e5|title=PRESS RELEASE: Dolphins Make Roster Moves|website=www.miamidolphins.com|access-date=2016-05-14}}</ref>

=== Oakland Raiders ===
On May 24, 2016, Herron signed to the [[Oakland Raiders]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.raiders.com/news/article-1/Oakland-Raiders-Sign-Wide-Receivers-Robert-Herron-and-Nathan-Palmer/8015d0fc-6235-4456-bb26-438237535a42|title=Oakland Raiders Sign Wide Receivers Robert Herron and Nathan Palmer|website=www.raiders.com|access-date=2016-05-24}}</ref> He was waived on May 26, 2016.

